title: Kaabil’s New Dialogue Promo | Hrithik Roshan Challenges Ronit Roy
text: tweet Here’s the new dialogue promo of the upcoming revenge action thriller Kaabil . The promo showcases Hrithik Roshan challenging the lead antagonist Ronit Roy by saying, “ Aaye Ga Na Darega Toh Nahi “. The film is a revenge drama and has been touted to be inspired from Daredevil. Watch this dialogue promo right here: Kaabil New Dialogue Promo | Hrithik Challenges Ronit Roy Directed by Sanjay Gupta, Kaabil also features Yami Gautam and Rohit Roy in key roles. The film is all set to clash with SRK’s Raees on 25th January. SHARE
